label: [OSC->3D] Open Sound Control to 3D
info:
### Description 

A 3D graphic representation of OSC (Open Source Control) generated by third party application.

### Requirements

This requirements the following Node-RED nodes:

- [node-red-contrib-web-babylonjs](https://flows.nodered.org/node/node-red-contrib-web-babylonjs)
- [Open Sound Control (OSC)](https://flows.nodered.org/node/node-red-contrib-osc)
- [introspection](https://flows.nodered.org/node/@gregoriusrippenstein/node-red-contrib-introspection) (optional)

### Related flows

- [Status Ticker](https://flowhub.org/f/18a539afac758c61) (i.e. using the node status colours as ticker)
- [Scroll pHAT ticker](https://flowhub.org/f/81d46dabe68094e4)
- [controlling a Scroll pHAT](https://flowhub.org/f/be2109bba90b6c5a)
- [OSC to I2C](https://flowhub.org/f/38021e5e2266e7e5)
